{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a Shopify section modeled after the 'Promotion Cards' section with enhanced flexibility and styling:

Layout:

Display a horizontal row of image cards, starting with 6 columns per row by default.

Allow the merchant to add as many columns (cards) as needed, with automatic wrapping based on screen size and available space.

Include settings to control how many columns are shown per device breakpoint (desktop, tablet, mobile).

Add section-wide settings for maximum width (full-width, wide, or constrained), padding, and spacing between cards.

Content elements per card:

Image (entire image should be clickable and link to a customizable URL)

Text overlaid at the bottom left of the image, including:

Heading (editable)

Optional subheading (editable)

Overlay settings:

Include an optional semi-transparent overlay behind the text at the bottom of each image

Theme editor controls should include:

Toggle to enable/disable overlay

Overlay opacity control (0%–100%)

Overlay height control (in pixels or % from the bottom of the image)

Mobile styling:

Allow full customization for mobile behavior, including:

Stack cards vertically or horizontally

Set different column count for mobile

Adjust padding, font sizes, and spacing

Ensure overlay and text remain legible on all devices

Theme editor customization settings:

Per-card controls for image, link, heading, and subheading

Section-wide controls for:

Number of columns per breakpoint

Overlay appearance (toggle, opacity, height)

Card size and spacing

Section max-width and alignment

Ensure performance best practices are followed: lazy-load images, include alt text fields, and apply responsive design standards for accessibility and speed., Add the following hover animation behavior to each image card:

On hover, apply a slight zoom-in and lift effect to the card (transform: scale(1.03) translateY(-4px)).

Increase overlay opacity slightly on hover to darken the image further (e.g., from 40% to 60%).

Apply a soft glow effect to the heading text on hover using text-shadow (e.g., 0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.8)).

Ensure transitions are smooth with a timing of ~300ms for all animated properties.

Include editor controls to toggle this animation on or off, and optionally adjust the glow intensity and lift distance.
, Give me an option to upload icon for each promotion card and give options to size it. Should be placed uppper lefthand corner of card
, For icon, it should be just the uploaded image, no conta

{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .promotion-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding }}px 0;
  }

  .promotion-cards__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_desktop }}, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_spacing }}px;
  }

  .promotion-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease, 
                box-shadow {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease;
  }

  {% if block.settings.enable_hover_animation %}
  .promotion-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: scale(1.03) translateY(-{{ block.settings.hover_lift_distance }}px);
    box-shadow: 0 {{ block.settings.hover_lift_distance }}px {{ block.settings.hover_lift_distance | times: 2 }}px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  {% endif %}

  .promotion-card__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 0;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.image_aspect_ratio }}%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .promotion-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease;
  }

  {% if block.settings.enable_hover_animation %}
  .promotion-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .promotion-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  {% endif %}

  .promotion-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 20px;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .promotion-card__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: {{ block.settings.icon_padding }}px;
    left: {{ block.settings.icon_padding }}px;
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: auto;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .promotion-card__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  {% if block.settings.enable_overlay %}
    .promotion-card__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: {{ block.settings.overlay_height }}%;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,{{ block.settings.overlay_opacity }}), rgba(0,0,0,0));
      z-index: 1;
      transition: background {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease;
    }
    
    {% if block.settings.enable_hover_animation %}
    .promotion-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .promotion-card__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,{{ block.settings.overlay_opacity | plus: 0.2 }}), rgba(0,0,0,0));
    }
    {% endif %}
  {% endif %}

  .promotion-card__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0 0 5px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    transition: text-shadow {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease;
  }

  {% if block.settings.enable_hover_animation %}
  .promotion-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .promotion-card__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-shadow: 0 0 {{ block.settings.text_glow_intensity }}px rgba(255,255,255,{{ block.settings.text_glow_opacity }});
  }
  {% endif %}

  .promotion-card__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .promotion-card__image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;}

  .promotion-card__image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 990px) {
    .promotion-cards__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_tablet }}, 1fr);
    }
    .promotion-card__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size | minus: 2 }}px;
    }
    
    .promotion-card__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_font_size | minus: 2 }}px;
    }
    
    .promotion-card__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .promotion-cards__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_mobile }}, 1fr);
    }
    
    .promotion-card__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size | minus: 4 }}px;
    }
    
    .promotion-card__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_font_size | minus: 2 }}px;
    }
    
    .promotion-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding | divided_by: 2 }}px 0;
    }
    
    .promotion-card__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="promotion-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="promotion-cards__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% for i in (1..block.settings.items) %}
      {% assign image_key = 'image_' | append: i %}
      {% assign icon_key = 'icon_' | append: i %}
      {% assign heading_key = 'heading_' | append: i %}
      {% assign subheading_key = 'subheading_' | append: i %}
      {% assign link_key = 'link_' | append: i %}
      
      {% assign image = block.settings[image_key] %}
      {% assign icon = block.settings[icon_key] %}
      {% assign heading = block.settings[heading_key] %}
      {% assign subheading = block.settings[subheading_key] %}
      {% assign link = block.settings[link_key] %}
      
      <a href="{{ link | default: '#' }}" class="promotion-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <div class="promotion-card__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if image != blank %}
            <img 
              src="{{ image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
              alt="{{ image.alt | escape }}"
              width="{{ image.width }}"
              height="{{ image.height }}"
              loading="lazy"
              class="promotion-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
          {% else %}
            <div class="promotion-card__image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
            </div>
          {% endif %}
          
          {% if icon != blank %}
            <div class="promotion-card__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <img 
                src="{{ icon | image_url: width: 200 }}"
                alt="{{ icon.alt | escape }}"
                width="{{ icon.width }}"
                height="{{ icon.height }}"
                loading="lazy"
              >
            </div>
          {% endif %}
          
          {% if block.settings.enable_overlay %}
            <div class="promotion-card__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        
        {% if heading != blank or subheading != blank %}
          <div class="promotion-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if heading != blank %}
              <h3 class="promotion-card__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ heading }}</h3>
            {% endif %}
            
            {% if subheading != blank %}
              <p class="promotion-card__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ subheading }}</p>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

